      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through them, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've talked to dozens of small business owners who spend their Sunday nights hunched over spreadsheets, manually stitching together next week's rota. They text employees one by one to confirm availability. They chase down no-shows. They re-calculate hours for payroll by hand.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That entire workflow is broken. And honestly, it doesn't have to be that way.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://shiftie.co"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shiftie",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is staff scheduling software that actually feels like it was built by people who've managed a team on a Saturday rush. It handles shift creation, availability management, attendance tracking, team messaging, and timesheet automation in one clean platform. No clunky modules you'll never open. No enterprise pricing that makes you wince.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through seven concrete use cases where Shiftie genuinely shines — and where I think it can save you the most time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 1: Building Weekly Rotas in Minutes, Not Hours",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the bread-and-butter use case, and it's where Shiftie earns its keep immediately.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Picture a café with 18 employees across two locations. The manager needs to account for part-time availability, full-time contracts, someone who only works mornings, and two students whose schedules change every semester. In a spreadsheet, that's a 45-minute puzzle every week. In Shiftie, you drag and drop shifts onto a visual calendar while the system flags conflicts in real time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The availability feature is key here. Employees submit their own availability through the app, and Shiftie keeps it front and center as you build the rota. You stop guessing. You stop texting. You stop getting that dreaded 6 AM \"I can't make it\" message.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-shiftie"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a detailed walkthrough, check our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step tutorial on how to use Shiftie",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.shiftie.co/t05s3i9e144c"
