      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use Case 6: Tracking Attendance Patterns Over Time",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of the under-the-radar use cases is using Shiftie's reporting tools to spot attendance trends.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Which employees regularly clock in late? Which shifts have the highest no-show rate? Are certain days consistently understaffed? Shiftie's reports surface this data without you having to manually track it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A venue manager I spoke with used Shiftie's attendance reports to identify that their Thursday evening shifts had a 30% tardiness rate. Turns out the shift started 30 minutes after a local bus route's gap. They adjusted start times by 15 minutes, and tardiness dropped to under 5%.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Data like that is hard to spot when you're drowning in manual scheduling. Shiftie makes it visible.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/shiftie-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to get more out of the platform? Our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Shiftie tips and best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " article has you covered.",
            "marks": []
