        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You sign up. You add your team. You build your first rota. The free 28-day trial gives you full access to every feature — employee scheduling, availability management, time clock, timesheets, team messaging, leave management, documents, reports, and multi-venue support. All of it. No feature gating.",
