        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pricing starts at £2.75 per employee per month, which is remarkably lean for what you get. And the UK-based support team is available seven days a week during your trial and beyond.",
